        public int loadKBPK(int slot,
                    java.lang.String kbpk,
                    android.os.Bundle extend)
             throws android.os.RemoteException
        KBPK and Master for AES are shared the same block & slots So, please use them without conflict
        Specified by:
        loadKBPK in interface IKLD
        Parameters:
        slot - the slot to inject the kbkp
        kbpk - the kbpk to be injected
        extend - KEY: overwrite(boolean), overwrite if not empty, otherwise return -1. KEY: checkValue(byte[]), the check value to verify the kbpk.
        Returns:
        0, success. -1, slot was injected a key, but not set overwrite or overwrite set to false. -2, inject failed, please if kbpk is correct or checkValue is correct.
        Throws:
        RemoteException
